DESCRIPTOR_JNDI_INITIAL_FACTORY

static final java.lang.String DESCRIPTOR_JNDI_INITIAL_FACTORY
This is the class name of our java.naming.factory.initial setting. Place this value in the Hashtable passed to "new InitialContext", or in the jndi.properties in your classpath.
